parcel.name: Residence at 5 Pastiche Terrace
parcel.description:
Large home with room to grow. Lots of extras ---

-family room and entertainment room
-mezzanine - could be a gym or home office
-side game room accessible - separate entrance
-upper floor bedroom suite with views
-motorbike
Swimming pool with diving board and boat dock.

Build includes furniture and images, can be moved around or removed - vox blocks are not moveable. 

Built by 4everKurious for Architect Island, Spring 2022.
